title: The Cackling Goose Market and Bakery Cafe
description: All vegetarian and gluten free cafe. Plenty of vegan options for lunch and baked goods. Menu and product available varies on a daily basis. Everything is made from scratch on site. They highly recommend their vegan grilled cheese sandwich and vegan mocha cake. The market stocks specialty foods, gluten-free, fair trade organic coffee, quality teas, raw nuts, dried fruits, fresh veggies, and more.
